      "text": "insert into purchased_contracts (user_id, contract_id, track_id)\nON CONFLICT\n    - notify the user they may have already purchased this contract\n        - confirm repurchase\n        - if yes -> comp-key + date.toString()\n        - if no -> DO NOTHING",
